_:Nbc80e6f1786d47fe8c10a3d57bfbd8a8 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>In October 2024, Alison was appointed as a non-executive director at Sellafield Ltd, chairing the Audit and Risk Assurance Committee.</p>\n\n<p>Alison holds a portfolio of non-executive roles, most recently as a non-executive committee member at the Department of Energy Security and Net Zero and as a non-executive director and audit committee chair at a large acute NHS Hospital Trust.  </p>\n\n<p>Alison’s career has spanned the private, public and charity sectors which has given her a breadth of experience from strategy and governance to transformation and stakeholder engagement.  </p>\n\n<p>After a successful career in the energy sector at Shell, Alison founded a start-up, working with high street retailers, to transform the sustainability of the cotton in our clothes.   </p>\n\n<p>Alison is a member of the Chartered Institute of Management Accountants (CIMA) and graduated in Physics and Materials Science from Cambridge University.  </p>\n\n<p>She is a Fellow of the RSA and a STEM Ambassador, encouraging more children to study “STEM” - Science, Technology, Engineering and Maths.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
